{"tid":1852723,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"［圍爐取暖］咁既時勢失緊業/想轉工既你點算？","createTime":"2020-01-30T14:43:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-30T15:39:32.000Z","uid":325200,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2efa6f03395e8ce5d33c148af4aa76ca0559c582","tid":1852723,"uid":325200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T14:43:30.000Z","msg":"公司今年無花紅 仲要人放無薪假 <br />\n搞到我好想轉工<br />\n但一諗到咁既時勢 分分鐘搵唔返依家份人工 <br />\n仲可能分分鐘工都搵唔到<br />\n依家個人好焦慮 身邊有frd發夢失業失到依家<br />\n本身有炒下散 依家cut人手連工都無埋<br />\n佢同我講依家搵工 搵極都無offer<br />\n連7仔都話唔請人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢咁既年紀去做m記又on99<br />\n所以想知搵緊工/打算轉工既你地有咩打算？"},{"pid":"b26a7a4f6f4aa6ab7ac0b1daa34c7081a1cbd3c0","tid":1852723,"uid":90955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T14:52:36.000Z","msg":"同問"},{"pid":"ebc965e427a55fdffd53d3fa39eb222b529ddcd2","tid":1852723,"uid":339864,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T14:53:28.000Z","msg":"同你差唔多，好想轉工 都係死頂，之前1111大三罷罷左幾日工差啲俾人炒，不過好彩最後冇事，依加咁嘅時勢揾工都好難<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，真係唔L洗諗轉工"},{"pid":"587fd5bac3ecbb84326bd1a3f8f3769cb258a596","tid":1852723,"uid":42762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T14:54:38.000Z","msg":"屌你老母我想轉工呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，好撚難頂"},{"pid":"bd16c7173b77e5a06a76b61c8294031259a911b6","tid":1852723,"uid":229369,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T15:16:17.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港警務處 全年招募</span></span></strong></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">警察招募組</span></div>"},{"pid":"5f8c3daf293c9d4d07cafc0ac1880010bb74f3a7","tid":1852723,"uid":82553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bd16c7173b77e5a06a76b61c8294031